  13,31,Ecx se Quran kauxz mont mov ter larm asunder dead parol (ili ne kred)! DI controls all AJX. Gxi ne temp believers est al don up realize ti DI willed Li direkt all popol? disbelievers ad sufer disasters consequence their own works hav disasters strik them di promes fulfilled DI testament NENIAM SXANGX predetermined destiny
