  13,33,Est tie any egal al Unu controls cxiu single anim? Ili set idols rival DI! Dir Nom them! Vi inform Him de io ter Li ne kon? Aux est vi fabricating empty statements? Ja schemes de those disbelieve ornam their okul! Ili tiel diverted dekstr path. Whomever DI send astray neniam trov direkt teacher
